gr.athenainnovation.imis.fusion.fetcher.geometry

Class GeometryProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • gr.athenainnovation.imis.fusion.fetcher.geometry.GeometryProcessor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EastingNorthingProcessor, GMLProcessor, LatLongProcessor, WKTProcessor

    public class GeometryProcessor
extends Object
    Container object for providing geometry processing functionality. This class cannot be instantiated and should be extended for each geometry type.
    Author:
    Thomas Maroulis
